snippet.title: Descenders Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Launching Feb 9 on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/681280/Descenders/
Descenders official site: http://www.descendersgame.com

Descenders is extreme downhill freeriding for the modern era, with procedurally generated worlds, and where mistakes have real consequences. Will you lead your team to glory and become the next legendary Descender?

-OUT NOW-

Developed by RageSquid
Published by No More Robots
Trailer music is Twist the Knife by Velcro Fly
https://velcrofly.bandcamp.com/
https://www.facebook.com/velcrofly.stonerrock
